Fortuna’s Lottery to Be Broadcast on CME’s Nova, Aktualne Says

-- B y   L a d k a   B a u e r o v a
-- 
2011-07-18T08:12:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-18/fortuna-s-lottery-to-be-broadcast-on-cme-s-nova-aktualne-says.html
Fortuna Entertainment Group NV (FORTUNA) , the
Czech betting company that sold shares last year, agreed to
broadcast its new lottery on  Central European Media Enterprises
Ltd. (CETV) ’s TV Nova channel,  Aktualne.cz  reported, citing a person
familiar with the talks.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ladka Bauerova in Prague at 
 lbauerova@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
